issue.title: Revamping PPAPI
issue.body:
- Updated PPAPI so that reading and writing values to memory and registers is easier and formalized
 - Reworked ADD and SUB in PPEXE to use updated PPAPI calls
 - Added PPCPU simulator in the PPAPI (don't need to have powerpoint, autohotkey, or win32com to test the PPCPU)
 - Fixed ADD and SUB
 - Simplified code inside PPAPI
